# lark-retro Demo — macOS Terminal 风格
# https://github.com/charmbracelet/vhs

Output assets/demo.gif

Set Theme "Pro"
Set FontFamily "Menlo"
Set FontSize 13
Set Width 860
Set Height 830
Set Padding 20
Set WindowBar Colorful
Set WindowBarSize 40
Set TypingSpeed 0ms
Set PlaybackSpeed 1

Type "bash demo/simulate.sh"
Enter
Sleep 15s
